This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Zabrimus
Project's homepage:          https://github.com/Zabrimus/vdr-plugin-webout
Latest version available at: https://github.com/Zabrimus/vdr-plugin-webout

